OL,3,CJury sworn in ahead of body parts
OL,4,Cmurder trial
OL,6,FA jury has been sworn in ahead of the
OL,7,Fmurder trial of a man accused of
OL,8,Fdismembering a man and dumping body
OL,9,Fparts across a city.
OL,11,FMarcin Majerkiewicz denies killing and
OL,12,Fdisposing of the body of Stuart
OL,13,FEverett, 67, who both lived in a house
OL,14,Fin the Winton area of Salford, Greater
OL,15,FManchester.
OL,17,FMajerkiewicz, 42, has pleaded not
OL,18,Fguilty to the murder and manslaughter
OL,19,Fof Mr Everett, between 24 March and 5
OL,20,FApril last year.
