OL,3,CJury sworn in ahead of body parts
OL,4,Cmurder trial
OL,6,FA jury of six women and six men was
OL,7,Fsworn in at Manchester Crown Court on
OL,8,FMonday 3 March with the trial, lasting
OL,9,Fup to four weeks, expected to begin
OL,10,Fwith the prosecution opening on
OL,11,FTuesday morning.
OL,13,FTrial judge Mr Justice Cavanagh told
OL,14,Fjurors, "This is an important and
OL,15,Fmajor case," as jurors were picked at
OL,16,Frandom from around 50 potential
OL,17,Fjurors, to hear the case.
