OL,6,FHe told the 12 jurors chosen the case
OL,7,Finvolved two counts, murder and
OL,8,Fmanslaughter, adding, "It may excite
OL,9,Fstrong emotions.
OL,11,F"Some of the evidence will be
OL,12,Fdistressing, however you must keep a
OL,13,Fcool head."
OL,15,FEarlier, jurors had been given a
OL,16,Fquestionnaire to ensure they could sit
OL,17,Ffor longer than the usual two-weeks
OL,18,Fjury service and to ensure they had no
OL,19,Fconnection to anyone involved in the
OL,20,Ftrial.
