OL,3,CJury sworn in ahead of body parts
OL,4,Cmurder trial
OL,6,FBen Campbell, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fjury panel: "This trial concerns the
OL,8,Fmurder of a male called Stuart
OL,9,FEverett, also known as Roman Ziemacki.
OL,11,F"It is the prosecution case that he
OL,12,Fwas murdered on March 27-28 last year,
OL,13,Fand his body was subsequently
OL,14,Fdismembered before being deposited
OL,15,Facross a number of different locations
OL,16,Fin the Manchester area.
