OL,6,F"Different parts of Stuart Everett's
OL,7,Fbody has since been recovered at the
OL,8,Ffollowing locations; Kersal Dale,
OL,9,FLinnyshaw Colliery Woods, Boggart Hole
OL,10,FClough, Blackleach Reservoir, Worsley
OL,11,FWoods and Chesterfield Close."
OL,13,FAfter the jury was sworn in, they were
OL,14,Fsent home to return on Tuesday morning
OL,15,Ffor the prosecution opening.
